      <li outputclass=\"contactnumber\">(029) 2074 2979/3877</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Quite modest changes in chemical structure can lead to changes in porphyrinogenicity but where possible general statements have been made about groups of drugs; these should be checked first.</p>
  </sectiondiv>
  <sectiondiv>
    <p outputclass=\"title\">Unsafe Drug Groups (check first)</p>
    <ul>
