        <p>
          <b>Fluticasone propionate:</b>
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <i>Adult and child over 12 years</i> 200–500 micrograms twice daily</li>
          <li>
            <i>Child 5–12 years </i> 100–200 micrograms twice daily</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <b>Mometasone furoate:</b>
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <i>Adult and child over 12 years</i> 400 micrograms twice daily</li>
          <li>
            <i>Child under 12 years</i> not recommended</li>
