                                                                                                      nicebnf:hasDitaContent """<section outputclass=\"adult\">
  <sectiondiv>
    <p outputclass=\"title\">Systemic corticosteroids</p>
    <p>Short-term treatment with corticosteroids can help to rapidly improve symptoms of rheumatoid arthritis. Long-term treatment in rheumatoid arthritis should be considered only after evaluating the risks and all other treatment options have been considered. Corticosteroids can induce osteoporosis, and prophylaxis should be considered on long-term treatment.</p>
