    <p outputclass=\"title\">Enteral nutrition in children</p>
    <p>Children have special requirements and in most situations liquid feeds prepared for adults are totally unsuitable—the advice of a paediatric dietitian should be sought.</p>
  </sectiondiv>
</section>"""^^<rdf:XMLLiteral> ; 
