          <li>the calcineurin inhibitor is not tolerated, particularly if nephrotoxicity endangers the transplanted kidney; <i>or</i></li>
          <li>there is very high risk of nephrotoxicity from the calcineurin inhibitor, requiring a reduction in the dose of the calcineurin inhibitor or its avoidance. </li>
